# Reindeer Rush - Simple Spec

christmas game

## Core Gameplay
Endless runner - reindeer auto-runs, tap to jump over obstacles, swipe down to duck under them. Speed increases gradually.

---

## Controls
- **Tap** = Jump
- **Swipe down** = Duck
- That's it!

---

## Obstacles
**Jump over:**
- Frozen ponds
- Snow boulders
- Gift boxes

**Duck under:**
- Icicles
- Tree branches

---

## Collectibles
- **Carrots** (10 pts) - common
- **Candy canes** (50 pts) - occasional
- **Stars** (100 pts) - rare

**One power-up:**
- **Shield bell** - survive one hit

---

## Sprites Needed (~20 total)
- Reindeer (run, jump, duck animations - 8 frames)
- 3-4 obstacle types
- 3 collectibles
- Simple scrolling background (mountains, trees)
- Ground tile

---

## Sounds (~8 total)
- Jump sound
- Land sound
- Collect item (ding!)
- Hit obstacle (bonk!)
- Background music (simple loop)
- Power-up chime

---

## Scoring
- Distance in meters (main score)
- Bonus points for collecting items
- High score saved

---

## Game Flow
1. Tap to start
2. Play until you crash
3. Show distance + score
4. Tap to restart

Simple, fun, 5-minute mini-game vibes!

---

## Visual & Input Notes
- The mobile canvas runs in landscape so the entire screen becomes the stage for a scenic snow valley; there are no button overlays, only the reindeer, terrain, and minimalistic score text when needed.
- Input relies on swipe gestures on the canvas: swipe up or tap to jump, swipe down to duck, with responsive physics and no distracting UI controls.
- The reindeer art takes precedenceâ€”prioritize a polished animated hero and supportive parallax background layers to create a lush shot of the holiday landscape.
